<p>Number of hours in a day =3D 24</p>

<p>Number of minutes in 1 hour =3D 60</p>

<p>Number of seconds in 1 minute =3D 60</p>

<p>So, number of seconds in 1 week =3D 60 =C3=97 60 =C3=97 24 =C3=97 7 =3D =
